                li Authoritative (Trombone, Piano, Guitar, Trumpet)
                li Bucolic (Flute, Cello)
                li Fragmented (Cello, Violin)
                li Chaotic (All soloists)
                li Earthy (Marimba)
                li Dusk (All soloists)

